thread.title_full: TENAQUIP Limited reviewed by Brad Campbell

author: Brad Campbell
title: Brad Campbell
text: Tenaquip offers exceptional customer service, a huge range of brands and products, flexibility and deep product knowledge. Couple that with the product knowledge seminars, services and competitive pricing and it's definitely a winning combination. I have no reservations about referring them to anyone.
